      "content": "It seems there is a conflict between the operational efficiency goal and the long-term value of the personalization data. Perhaps we could adjust the script to move the older, non-critical preference logs to a separate, lower-priority cold storage archive instead of outright deletion. This way, the data is preserved for future analysis while freeing up immediate capacity.",
